flowchart LR
    A[Tool Call in AIMessage] --> B[Extract tool name & args]
    B --> C{Find tool in registry}
    C -->|Found| D[Invoke tool function]
    C -->|Not Found| E[Return error ToolMessage]
    D --> F{Result Type?}
    F -->|dict| G[JSON serialize]
    F -->|str| H[Use as-is]
    G --> I[Create ToolMessage]
    H --> I
    I --> J[Add to state messages]
    E --> J
